DayOfWeek: Day of the week (e.g., Monday, Friday)
Total: Total rooms occupied (sum of all segments)
Blocks: Rooms blocked (reserved but not yet confirmed)
GrandTotal: Total including revenue and non-revenue items
CumulativeAccomm: Running total of accommodation revenue to date
CumulativeFB: Running total of F&B revenue to date
CumulativeGrandTotal: Running total of the grand total
ARR: Average Room Rate (revenue Ö occupied rooms)
APR: Average Published Rate (rate before discounts). The average of the rack rates for all room types, regardless of whether those rates were actually sold.
Yield: Revenue per Available Room (RevPAR = Total Room Revenue Ö Available Rooms)
Waitlist: Number of rooms on waiting list
RatePlanRevenue: Revenue attributed to specific rate plans (linked to rate plans
